  "description": "In [card games](../index.md), a wild card is a card that can substitute for other identities under specified conditions. The holder of a wild card declares what [rank](./rank.md) and [suit](./suit.md) it represents, allowing it to complete combinations that would otherwise be impossible given the cards actually dealt.",
